(thirdQuint)Prevention of Traumatic Brain Injury in Youth and Adolescents.

 The overarching goal of this project is to reduce traumatic brain injury in children and adolescents by promoting bicycle helmet use via an inpatient educational program.

 The Safe Kids East Central injury prevention educational program was customized for hospitalized subjects and their caregivers.

 The investigators hypothesized that this program would increase bicycle helmet use.

